        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【#做手术前哪些生活习惯要改变#[可怜]】做手术是场“大考”，身体状态良好才能确保手术顺利进行和术后康复。[话筒]医生提醒，做手术前这些生活习惯得改改👇�...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%81%9A%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%AF%E5%89%8D%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E4%B9%A0%E6%83%AF%E8%A6%81%E6%94%B9%E5%8F%98%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%81%9A%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%AF%E5%89%8D%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E4%B9%A0%E6%83%AF%E8%A6%81%E6%94%B9%E5%8F%98%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#做手术前哪些生活习惯要改变#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[可怜]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_kelian-a9df4278bf.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】做手术是场“大考”，身体状态良好才能确保手术顺利进行和术后康复。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>医生提醒，做手术前这些生活习惯得改改👇🏻<br><br>✅戒烟：长期吸烟会增加手术麻醉的风险，戒烟8周以上可最大程度减少影响；<br><br>✅减重：肥胖患者麻醉药物用量大、代谢慢，较厚的脂肪会增加手术难度，也更易出现并发症；<br><br>✅保证合理膳食、规律作息等。<br><br>这些知识，你得知道，但小卫希望你们永远也用不到！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[太阳]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/w_taiyang-2b1d91ddac.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视新闻）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4944754945753111" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hhsie8un8rj616c1kg1ky02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/nERg8ORUlx088w1fWwMM01041200sJs50E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=720x1280.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1694621853&amp;ssig=C69yVv1eBI&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/N4IWmfXElx088w1fV9YI01041200gJch0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=540x960.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1694621853&amp;ssig=cJyXcT%2FA6X&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/3im5X7hYlx088w1fSWJq010412008Sxl0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=360x640.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1694621853&amp;ssig=4XeaHODVuo&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4944754945753111" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
